data.description: VA Assumable Loan with 2.369% interest rate available to Vets/those with VA Entitlement!! Ask agent for more details.  All other forms of financing also accepted. This charming 2-level Colonial is situated on a generous 1/3 acre lot that is flat and oh-so-usable. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 updated bathrooms, this home is a fabulous investment.  Major updates include a new roof (Oct 2023) and HVAC (Feb 2022)! The heart of the home is undoubtedly the spacious kitchen, which seamlessly flows into the large gathering and dining areas. Equipped with Stainless Steel appliances and a convenient breakfast bar, this kitchen is perfect for both everyday cooking and entertaining. The kitchen is open to a room that as suitable as Dining or gathering space, and features a large brick hearth and a fireplace with a wood stove insert, promising cozy evenings during the colder months.  Access your private deck from the sliding glass door where you can unwind and enjoy outdoor dining. As you step out to your back yard  you'll immediately appreciate the expansive, flat, and entirely usable space. Enclosed by a full privacy fence, it offers a peaceful haven for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying the great outdoors.  The L-shaped great room off the kitchen boasts attractive hardwood floors and has flexibility for a host of uses.   Before heading upstairs you'll notice a conveniently-located laundry room off the kitchen, and a powder room at the base of the hardwood staircase.  The upper level features 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The extra-large primary suite is a true retreat, featuring a sitting/reading area, an updated bathroom with a stylish 2-sink vanity and a luxurious walk-in shower, and a walk-in closet. The primary suite, along with the hallway and one other bedroom, showcases beautiful hardwood floors, adding a touch of elegance to the living spaces. Meanwhile, the remaining two bedrooms provide cozy comfort with plush carpeting underfoot.  The hall bath has also been updated The home offers plenty of storage with a two-car garage and a large shed.   Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming Colonial your own, offering a blend of comfort, convenience, and outdoor serenity. Residents of Montclair have access to a multitude of amenities, including a 109-acre stocked lake with three sandy beaches, a boat ramp, boat storage, fishing piers, playgrounds, tot lots, ball fields, exercise stations, and a new dog park. The community also boasts an 18-hole golf course with a full-service Country Club, and pool memberships are available. Convenient access to I-95 and nearby commuter lots and bus routes simplify commuting to DC, the Pentagon, and beyond. Special financing is available through Project My Home, offering potential savings on closing costs. Additionally, the home is currently enrolled in a premium home warranty, which can be transferred to the buyer at closing.
